OL,3,CFire service rescues pony stuck in
OL,4,Ccattle grid after walkers left gate
OL,5,Copen
OL,7,FA woman from Crickhowell is calling on
OL,8,Fwalkers to follow the countryside code
OL,9,Fafter her pony got stuck in a cattle
OL,10,Fgrid.
OL,12,FBeth Watkins' 21-year-old pony Teifi
OL,13,Fhad became trapped after escaping his
OL,14,Fpaddock when walkers left a gate open.
OL,16,FCrews from were called to the incident
OL,17,Fin Llangatwg, Powys, on 5 March and it
OL,18,Ftook four hours to free the animal.
