OL,7,FA spokesperson for the service said:
OL,8,F"To avoid Teifi becoming distressed,
OL,9,Fthe vet who was also in attendance
OL,10,Fsedated him and crews proceeded to
OL,11,Futilise road traffic collision and
OL,12,Fanimal rescue equipment to release him
OL,13,Ffrom the cattle grid."
OL,15,FFollowing the rescue, Ms Watkins said
OL,16,FTeifi is "recovering well" but said
OL,17,F"it could have been so much worse".
