OL,7,FPosting on social media, she
OL,8,Fcontinued: "Please think when you open
OL,9,Fgates on private property. Close them
OL,10,Fbehind you.
OL,12,F"As you can see, the support we
OL,13,Freceived was incredible and we can't
OL,14,Fdescribe how grateful we are, but this
OL,15,Fis the Fire Brigade and the time they
OL,16,Fspent with us might have been needed
OL,17,Felsewhere."
