OL,7,FThe Countryside Code urges all those
OL,8,Fwho use the countryside, coast, parks
OL,9,Fand waterways to always leave gates
OL,10,Fand property as they are found and to
OL,11,Ffollow instructions on signs.
OL,13,FFarmers and landowners may close gates
OL,14,Fto keep animals in or leave them open
OL,15,Fto give access to food and water.
